§ 5732. Transferred Editorial Notes Codification Section 5732 was editorially reclassified as section 11277 of Title 34, Crime Control and Law Enforcement.
Prior ProvisionsA prior section 5732, Pub. L. 93–415, title III, § 322, Sept. 7, 1974, 88 Stat. 1132, set forth restrictions on disclosure and transfer of records, prior to repeal by Pub. L. 95–115, § 7(b), Oct. 3, 1977, 91 Stat. 1058, eff. Oct. 1, 1977.
